## Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|-----------|
| Model | PyTorch 2.3, EfficientNet-B0, torchvision |
| Backend | FastAPI, Uvicorn, Pillow, OpenCV |
| Frontend | HTML5, CSS3, Vanilla JS |
| Visualization | Matplotlib, Seaborn |
| Evaluation | scikit-learn |